  "title": "Cobblemon: Simple Smart Healer",
  "description": "Adds a simple device that heals your entire Pokémon team wherever you are.",
  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Cobblemon : Smart Healer</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1444769/description_e00a5ef3-9473-4b11-8640-13593395d73e.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.7.1-Cobblemon-brightgreen\" width=\"139\" height=\"24\"></a><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architectury-api\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/13.0.8-ArchitecturyAPI-red\" width=\"168\" height=\"24\"></a><a href=\"https://neoforged.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1-NeoForge-darkred\" width=\"125\" height=\"24\"></a><a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/1.21.1-Fabric-blue\" width=\"103\" height=\"24\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Tired of having to return home to heal your Pok&eacute;mon in the middle of an expedition?</strong><br><strong>This mod adds a simple device that can heal your entire Pok&eacute;mon team at once.</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Just right-click anywhere while holding the device, and your team is healed. There is no recharge time; just use it.</strong></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CRAFT DEVICE</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1444769/description_53992f4e-f7ee-4dfe-bc0e-f45b83944a2a.png\" width=\"301\" height=\"150\"></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SIMPLE 3D MODEL.</strong></h3>\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1444769/description_8371cc1d-f75d-4eb6-a08c-0dd0ac03d0cf.png\"></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>",
